  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The leader of Madu Tamil Sentinel Organization is released on bail",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ganavathipillai Mohan, leader of the Batticaloa Tamil Sensational Organisation, who was arrested under the Prevention of Terrorism Act, has been released.",
        "He was arrested under the Prevention of Terrorism Act in 2021 on charges of uploading pictures of the banned LTTE organization on websites.",
        "In this case, today Friday (29) he has been released on bail with a bond of Rs.",
        "Ganavathipillai Mohan was arrested by the Ebravur police under the Prevention of Terrorism Act on May 3 last on the charge of uploading banned LTTE images on websites.",
        "After the arrested person was produced in the Edravur Tourism Court, he was kept under remand.",
        "In this case, after Attorney R. Jeyasingham and Chinnathurai Jagan, who are counsels of the President of the Legislative Assembly, appeared today on Friday and filed the Munnagar bond at the Ebravur Tourism Court, the Additional Judge of the Tourism Court S. Anwar Sadat was released on bail after trial."
      ],
